#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.update.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.update"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:1 of
msgid "Modify in place using non-NA values from another DataFrame."
msgstr "使用另一个 DataFrame 中的非 NA 值就地修改。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:3 of
msgid "Aligns on indices. There is no return value."
msgstr "按索引对齐。无返回值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:5 of
msgid ""
"Should have at least one matching index/column label with the original "
"DataFrame. If a Series is passed, its name attribute must be set, and "
"that will be used as the column name to align with the original "
"DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"应至少有一个与原始 DataFrame 匹配的索引/列标签。如果传递的是 Series，必须"
"设置其 name 属性，该属性将用作与原始 DataFrame 对齐的列名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:10 of
msgid ""
"Only left join is implemented, keeping the index and columns of the "
"original object."
msgstr "仅实现左连接，保留原始对象的索引和列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:13 of
msgid ""
"How to handle non-NA values for overlapping keys:  * True: overwrite "
"original DataFrame's values   with values from `other`. * False: only "
"update values that are NA in   the original DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"如何处理重叠键的非 NA 值：  * True：使用 `other` 中的值覆盖原始 DataFrame"
" 的值。 * False：仅更新原始 DataFrame 中为 NA 的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:13 of
msgid "How to handle non-NA values for overlapping keys:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:15 of
msgid "True: overwrite original DataFrame's values with values from `other`."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:17 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "False: only update values that are NA in the original DataFrame."
msgstr "如果 `other` 包含 NaN，则原始 DataFrame 中对应的值不会被更新。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:20 of
msgid ""
"Can choose to replace values other than NA. Return True for values that "
"should be updated."
msgstr "可以选择替换除 NA 以外的值。对于应该更新的值返回 True。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:23 of
msgid ""
"If 'raise', will raise a ValueError if the DataFrame and `other` both "
"contain non-NA data in the same place."
msgstr ""
"如果为 'raise'，当 DataFrame 和 `other` 在相同位置都包含非 NA 数据时将"
"引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:27 of
msgid "This method directly changes calling object."
msgstr "此方法直接更改调用对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:30 of
msgid ""
"* When `errors='raise'` and there's overlapping non-NA data.     * When "
"`errors` is not either `'ignore'` or `'raise'`"
msgstr ""
"* 当 `errors='raise'` 且存在重叠的非 NA 数据时。     * 当 `errors` 不是 `"
"'ignore'` 或 `'raise'` 时"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:30 of
msgid ""
"When `errors='raise'` and there's overlapping non-NA data.     * When "
"`errors` is not either `'ignore'` or `'raise'`"
msgstr ""
"当 `errors='raise'` 且存在重叠的非 NA 数据时。     * 当 `errors` 不是 `'"
"ignore'` 或 `'raise'` 时"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:31 of
msgid "* If `join != 'left'`"
msgstr "* 如果 `join != 'left'`"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:31 of
msgid "If `join != 'left'`"
msgstr "如果 `join != 'left'`"

