#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:56 of
msgid ""
"The DataFrame's length does not increase as a result of the update, only "
"values at matching index/column labels are updated."
msgstr "由于更新，DataFrame 的长度不会增加，只有匹配索引/列标签的值会被更新。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:79 of
msgid "For Series, its name attribute must be set."
msgstr "对于 Series，必须设置其 name 属性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.update.df_update:91 of
msgid ""
"If `other` contains NaNs the corresponding values are not updated in the "
"original dataframe."
msgstr "如果 `other` 包含 NaN，则原始 DataFrame 中对应的值不会被更新。"

